    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><mark>This paper is a great example that in order for you to make an impact, it’s more important that you</mark><mark> focus more on the quality of your paper</mark><mark> rather than the length.</mark> There’s no point in making the paper unnecessarily lengthy if the primary gist of the research is missing or is somewhat vague.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
